WEBVTT

00:00:02.080 --> 00:00:06.798
Hi, my name is Brandon, and

00:00:06.799 --> 00:00:08.959
I have had an experience with the Lord that he

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:10.638
keeps telling me

00:00:10.639 --> 00:00:12.879
I need to tell people about.

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:15.758
I've never really talked in front of a camera before

00:00:15.759 --> 00:00:18.639
like this, but he wanted me to

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:22.959
document it and

00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:25.358
tell everybody what happened and what kind of

00:00:25.359 --> 00:00:27.919
experience I had with him.

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:34.190
This experience lasted all night long, and

00:00:34.719 --> 00:00:37.519
I'm just asking the Holy Spirit right now to help me communicate

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:42.630
everything that I saw.

00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:45.839
It's really important because Jesus Christ is coming, and he told me

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:49.078
he's coming face to face.

00:00:49.079 --> 00:00:53.439
This experience happened on July

00:00:53.440 --> 00:00:55.799
6th,

00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:59.198
2014, and

00:00:59.199 --> 00:01:01.198
I've held it all these years. I wrote it down on paper and

00:01:01.199 --> 00:01:03.038
released it to some people on Facebook

00:01:03.039 --> 00:01:08.519
and to some church friends and family.

00:01:08.520 --> 00:01:12.559
Some people received it and some

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:18.149
people didn't. I'm just a

00:01:18.479 --> 00:01:24.599
deliverer of the message that he gave me. I'm not here to argue about

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:28.679
theology or

00:01:28.680 --> 00:01:32.239
try to convince anybody of

00:01:32.240 --> 00:01:34.639
my experience.

00:01:34.640 --> 00:01:37.629
I'm going to tell you exactly what happened, exactly how it

00:01:37.630 --> 00:01:37.639
happened,

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:41.199
from the beginning to

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:43.158
the end.

00:01:43.159 --> 00:01:46.239
I don't know if you're a mid-tribulation,

00:01:46.240 --> 00:01:53.230
post-tribulation, or pre-tribulation believer.

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:57.639
Like I said, I'm not here

00:01:57.640 --> 00:02:00.879
to argue or try to get you to say

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:05.270
anything in the comments about

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:10.079
what I saw or what I experienced. I'm just telling you what I saw and

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:12.199
we'll go from there.

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:18.630
It all started out while I was asleep;

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:21.999
I went to bed a normal night, nothing different. I went to sleep

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:24.639
and in the middle of my sleep, all of

00:02:24.640 --> 00:02:27.359
a sudden,

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:30.479
I don't know if I was in my body or out of my body.

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:35.509
I don't know how it happened; all

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:39.598
I know is all of a sudden I was standing with Jesus,

00:02:39.599 --> 00:02:42.878
and he was on my right hand the whole time in this experience.

00:02:42.879 --> 00:02:46.598
He grabbed a hold of my hand and

00:02:46.599 --> 00:02:51.919
I'll go from there. The first

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:55.759
scene, per se, of what I saw was

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:57.759
Jesus

00:02:57.760 --> 00:03:02.390
standing on my right hand. He had a hold of my hand and we

00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:05.919
were in a town. I don't know what town we were in, but

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:08.719
I know that there was a big white building over to the

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:12.318
side.

00:03:12.319 --> 00:03:14.709
I was looking up at this big white building and

00:03:14.710 --> 00:03:14.719
at

00:03:14.720 --> 00:03:17.349
the sky, and

00:03:17.350 --> 00:03:17.359
the sky

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:20.479
was alive. It was like it was

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:23.679
moving; it was full

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:26.958
of lightning and very

00:03:26.959 --> 00:03:31.598
spooky looking. I looked out over the

00:03:31.599 --> 00:03:33.919
horizon and

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:37.439
there was this lady running towards me, and she started

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:39.679
screaming. They were all

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:41.679
screaming in terror; they were all freaking out.

00:03:41.680 --> 00:03:44.878
It was incredible.

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:48.719
They were saying,

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:51.759
"They're gone. They're gone."I said, "Who's gone?"I

00:03:51.760 --> 00:03:53.439
told this lady,

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:56.798
"Who's gone?"and she said, "Did you

00:03:56.799 --> 00:03:59.039
not see?"I

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:00.719
said, "Did I not see what, ma'am? What are you

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:02.878
talking about?"At

00:04:02.879 --> 00:04:05.669
this time, she could see me. Now, not every

00:04:05.670 --> 00:04:07.680
time in this experience were people able to see me.

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:16.399
In this instance,

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:19.518
she could not see Jesus, but she could see me.

00:04:19.519 --> 00:04:22.399
She said, "The aliens?

00:04:22.400 --> 00:04:25.079
The aliens came and got the Christians."I

00:04:25.080 --> 00:04:28.478
said, "The aliens?"She

00:04:28.479 --> 00:04:30.239
said, "Yes, they all

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:35.070
disappeared. They went up."At

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:41.110
that moment, she just ran off. She was frantic, screaming in terror. She

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:43.478
ran as fast as she could,

00:04:43.479 --> 00:04:46.719
panicking. I looked out over the

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:51.189
horizon of the city. I was up on a

00:04:51.639 --> 00:04:55.039
hill at this time and I could see everything on fire. Everything was on fire—the

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:57.918
cars, the houses, the

00:04:57.919 --> 00:05:02.559
buildings. It

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:04.719
was like chaos beyond anything you could ever

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:07.599
comprehend was happening at this time.

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:12.478
You could smell the smoke.

00:05:12.479 --> 00:05:14.159
People were looting; they were stealing out of cars and

00:05:14.160 --> 00:05:15.519
buildings. They were

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:18.319
trashing the city

00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:22.399
where I was. Jesus

00:05:22.400 --> 00:05:26.079
didn't say anything. In fact, he never spoke;

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:30.790
I could perceive his thoughts when he

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:33.908
was touching my hand. I knew what he was thinking, but he never said anything out of his mouth. He could

00:05:33.909 --> 00:05:35.919
understand what I was thinking, but I never said anything to

00:05:41.919 --> 00:05:44.399
him. I was just looking across the city, thinking,

00:05:44.400 --> 00:05:49.430
"Oh my gosh, what is going on?"All

00:05:51.919 --> 00:05:55.439
of a sudden, we translated. We left

00:05:55.440 --> 00:05:58.319
that spot and went to another spot. He grabbed my hand—we

00:05:58.320 --> 00:06:01.990
were still holding hands—but it was like

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:04.839
we just disappeared and

00:06:04.840 --> 00:06:10.670
came to another time. In this time frame, I

00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:13.989
was looking over Europe. I knew I

00:06:13.990 --> 00:06:15.519
was looking over Europe

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:17.599
because I was standing back, like I was watching a

00:06:17.600 --> 00:06:19.999
movie. It was very strange.

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:24.519
I was looking out over Europe and

00:06:24.520 --> 00:06:29.279
I saw this man in Berlin.

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:32.308
All the world leaders were behind a table. It was a round table in Berlin. It looked like a big office. It was

00:06:32.309 --> 00:06:34.319
a brown table, and there were chairs all around it. All of these world leaders were behind

00:06:45.840 --> 00:06:49.748
this big table, and

00:06:49.749 --> 00:06:49.758
this man—I

00:06:49.759 --> 00:06:51.918
didn't know who he

00:06:51.919 --> 00:06:54.879
was at the time, but

00:06:54.880 --> 00:06:57.758
I'll tell you later—and

00:06:57.759 --> 00:07:01.989
all of the people were asking him for help. They

00:07:01.990 --> 00:07:01.999
were asking him for

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:04.159
a solution to

00:07:04.160 --> 00:07:06.399
all the rioting and

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:10.879
the craziness that was going on. He

00:07:10.880 --> 00:07:14.239
was instructing them on what to do. He had

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:18.159
all the wisdom and

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:20.799
was very powerful in demeanor, the way he carried

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:26.790
himself. He was wearing a gray suit, and

00:07:27.520 --> 00:07:32.638
he was a Middle Eastern man. All of a sudden, that

00:07:32.639 --> 00:07:37.279
scene was over, but

00:07:37.280 --> 00:07:39.908
the Lord at that time spoke to me about a scripture and

00:07:39.909 --> 00:07:41.919
showed me

00:07:42.560 --> 00:07:44.959
how everyone

00:07:44.960 --> 00:07:48.159
would give over their kingdoms to him within one hour. As

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:50.198
I said, I'm not a Bible

00:07:50.199 --> 00:07:53.679
scholar or

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:56.799
a theology major; I'm just a guy who loves Jesus

00:07:56.800 --> 00:07:59.279
and seeks Him with all my

00:07:59.280 --> 00:08:01.359
heart, and I had

00:08:01.360 --> 00:08:04.439
this experience with Him.

00:08:04.440 --> 00:08:09.349
The next scene I see is

00:08:09.350 --> 00:08:09.359
this man

00:08:09.360 --> 00:08:13.439
on TV—he's

00:08:13.440 --> 00:08:17.439
on CNN, Fox, and

00:08:17.440 --> 00:08:20.559
everywhere. He is telling all the people

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:24.239
of the world what happened to the

00:08:24.240 --> 00:08:26.719
people who disappeared,

00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:31.598
explaining

00:08:31.599 --> 00:08:34.079
that they were rebellious, that

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:36.759
they were taken away out of

00:08:36.760 --> 00:08:39.119
rebellion, and that they were being

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:41.038
punished. All these people were punished—it

00:08:41.039 --> 00:08:43.199
was the Christians, and they

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:44.799
were all being

00:08:44.800 --> 00:08:47.439
taken out. Then he

00:08:47.440 --> 00:08:49.278
explained that he was the new leader of

00:08:49.279 --> 00:08:55.990
the world. I looked out and saw

00:08:59.360 --> 00:09:04.150
how he was gradually taking power. I want to tell

00:09:05.279 --> 00:09:07.439
you what I

00:09:07.440 --> 00:09:12.070
felt;

00:09:12.360 --> 00:09:14.958
this is very important: everybody wakes up every

00:09:14.959 --> 00:09:17.639
single day with a peace

00:09:17.640 --> 00:09:20.999
they don't realize

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:24.398
they have. They go to bed with it and

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:26.398
wake up with it. Even the worst

00:09:26.399 --> 00:09:30.879
sinner in the world has a form of

00:09:30.880 --> 00:09:33.559
peace inside of them that they don't

00:09:33.560 --> 00:09:39.230
even realize. When the rapture

00:09:40.360 --> 00:09:45.599
happens and we're taken out, there is

00:09:45.600 --> 00:09:49.919
a void of peace like I've never felt in all of my life; it

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:54.829
blankets the

00:09:55.600 --> 00:09:59.119
earth. I used to think that the Holy Spirit left with us because He dwells in

00:09:59.120 --> 00:10:00.958
each Christian. He dwells in us,

00:10:00.959 --> 00:10:03.599
and when we invite him into our heart,

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:05.999
I believe that he went with us when

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:08.639
the rapture happened. I cannot

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:10.999
back that up biblically. I don't

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:15.278
know. All I know

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:19.159
is that there is no prayer covering, there is no sense of

00:10:19.160 --> 00:10:22.559
peace, there is no joy.

00:10:22.560 --> 00:10:24.278
It is absolute

00:10:24.279 --> 00:10:29.310
chaos. And this

00:10:31.600 --> 00:10:36.389
man has a sense that whenever everybody looks at him, when everybody is

00:10:36.519 --> 00:10:40.319
gazing upon him, a false sense of peace is what I

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:43.599
want to say.

00:10:43.600 --> 00:10:46.709
He brings a peace when he is on the TV. He

00:10:46.710 --> 00:10:46.719
brings a

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:52.949
sense of comfort that

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:56.870
everybody wants to follow him so quickly because they are so scared and everybody

00:10:57.839 --> 00:11:01.278
is so tormented. They all turn to him so quickly out of that peace that

00:11:01.279 --> 00:11:03.999
he brings, but it is dirty.

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:06.599
I don't know how to describe it.

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:10.559
So he is on the TV, and he

00:11:10.560 --> 00:11:13.838
is telling everybody what happened to

00:11:13.839 --> 00:11:17.879
the Christians.

00:11:17.880 --> 00:11:20.039
Then I see people in the

00:11:20.040 --> 00:11:23.669
Iran and Iraq area over there—Pakistan,

00:11:23.670 --> 00:11:25.680
that area over there—they

00:11:26.279 --> 00:11:29.838
were rejoicing. And they were all calling out

00:11:29.839 --> 00:11:33.919
and saying the Mahdi has come. The Mahdi

00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:36.319
has come. And I don't know what

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:39.439
that means.

00:11:39.440 --> 00:11:42.719
I have studied it now a little bit more.

00:11:42.720 --> 00:11:44.239
I don't know what I'm

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:47.039
allowed to say about all this

00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:49.599
as far as on YouTube and what

00:11:49.600 --> 00:11:51.679
will be allowed. I don't want my

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:54.879
video to get flagged, but they were calling it the Mahdi.

00:11:54.880 --> 00:11:56.669
They were calling him the Mahdi. And so

00:11:56.670 --> 00:11:56.679
everybody was calling him the Mahdi.

00:11:56.680 --> 00:12:01.350
And so he was

00:12:06.639 --> 00:12:10.239
himself Middle Eastern. He was a Muslim. I know this because he said he was and he

00:12:10.240 --> 00:12:16.470
had a... Okay, I won't get

00:12:17.279 --> 00:12:22.799
to that part yet. Okay, this is what happens next. I see him come on TV, and he

00:12:22.800 --> 00:12:25.599
is telling

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:28.559
everybody to bring their Bibles into

00:12:28.560 --> 00:12:32.870
the stadiums, into these areas. He said, 'If you see a

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:36.479
Bible, it is mandated by law that everybody brings these Bibles into these areas.'And

00:12:36.480 --> 00:12:42.350
so, it was like courthouses,

00:12:42.959 --> 00:12:45.559
places like that. They were all like police stations, things like

00:12:45.560 --> 00:12:49.199
that. He brings these Bibles in and they

00:12:49.200 --> 00:12:52.879
start stacking them up—big

00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:54.719
shelves full. There were

00:12:54.720 --> 00:12:57.359
thousands, millions of Bibles just everywhere. And

00:12:57.360 --> 00:12:59.838
everybody just willfully

00:12:59.839 --> 00:13:01.518
did it; they just brought

00:13:01.519 --> 00:13:03.359
in the Bibles. And

00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:06.629
I remember seeing them everywhere. There were stacks and

00:13:07.600 --> 00:13:10.559
stacks of Bibles everywhere. And so they would write down your name on a piece of

00:13:10.560 --> 00:13:14.710
paper of who brought the Bible and what

00:13:14.720 --> 00:13:17.439
it was or whatever. And he told everybody, 'If you want to

00:13:17.440 --> 00:13:19.199
come and check out the Bible and look at it, it is

00:13:19.200 --> 00:13:22.159
okay.'We'll let you. It was kind of

00:13:22.160 --> 00:13:24.398
a trick, though, because whenever

00:13:24.399 --> 00:13:28.078
people came in and wrote on

00:13:28.079 --> 00:13:32.069
the paper to check out their Bible that they brought in—if they wanted to look at it

00:13:34.720 --> 00:13:38.559
again—you were marked even more so. And so it was

00:13:38.560 --> 00:13:41.518
like you were

00:13:41.519 --> 00:13:43.199
being watched. It was a surveillance

00:13:43.200 --> 00:13:48.710
state. It was really weird. It

00:13:48.720 --> 00:13:51.199
was like a library, is what I want to call it. Within a couple

00:13:51.200 --> 00:13:56.439
of months, I would say I saw

00:13:56.440 --> 00:14:03.430
a football field with piles of Bibles,

00:14:03.760 --> 00:14:06.159
probably three or four stories high. It was massive—just

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:09.198
massive. They were all being burned. All the

00:14:09.199 --> 00:14:12.879
Bibles were burned by his order.

00:14:12.880 --> 00:14:16.958
Like I said,

00:14:16.959 --> 00:14:20.159
the gasoline was all over them. They were thrown into the fire, and

00:14:20.160 --> 00:14:22.319
it was incredible. Just massive amounts of smoke and the Bibles

00:14:22.320 --> 00:14:24.919
all burning.

00:14:24.920 --> 00:14:34.230
Then I saw these flags

00:14:34.639 --> 00:14:36.958
that he put on every single courthouse. If you had a country flag, like the

00:14:36.959 --> 00:14:38.719
United States of America or Europe,

00:14:38.720 --> 00:14:41.359
those flags were taken down

00:14:41.360 --> 00:14:44.879
and his flag was put up.

00:14:44.880 --> 00:14:50.790
It was black,

00:14:51.760 --> 00:14:56.599
green, and white, and it had

00:14:56.600 --> 00:15:00.469
these gold swords that were all in the center of

00:15:00.470 --> 00:15:02.480
it—massive swords,

00:15:03.720 --> 00:15:09.189
like a

00:15:11.519 --> 00:15:13.518
saber, is what I want to call it. It

00:15:13.519 --> 00:15:17.350
was a massive sword in

00:15:19.279 --> 00:15:21.039
the center of this thing, and each color represented

00:15:21.040 --> 00:15:27.590
a terrorist group, ISIS

00:15:28.920 --> 00:15:32.159
and others. I'm not going to even

00:15:32.160 --> 00:15:34.398
go there because

00:15:34.399 --> 00:15:38.389
I don't know all their names, but

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:46.870
each was a terrorist group,

00:15:47.600 --> 00:15:52.159
and they're all being thanked for bringing in his reign

00:15:52.160 --> 00:15:57.030
because they supported this so much.

00:15:59.720 --> 00:16:05.749
After that,

00:16:07.720 --> 00:16:11.758
he puts his flag on the

00:16:11.759 --> 00:16:15.679
buildings, and then

00:16:15.680 --> 00:16:18.398
this is what happens next. I go

00:16:18.399 --> 00:16:21.198
with Jesus to this other area. In this, I

00:16:21.199 --> 00:16:26.799
see

00:16:26.800 --> 00:16:31.749
people on Fridays. Every Friday, you're required to worship him. Every

00:16:33.120 --> 00:16:36.239
Friday, they all had white outfits on. Every person in the world was required

00:16:36.240 --> 00:16:39.679
to wear a white outfit, and they had

00:16:39.680 --> 00:16:44.389
white garments on their heads. The women

00:16:45.120 --> 00:16:47.838
did. And men had white garments on their heads. They had white robes on and they were

00:16:47.839 --> 00:16:51.679
all in single file lines.

00:16:51.680 --> 00:16:55.439
Every line was

00:16:55.440 --> 00:17:00.239
perfect and they were all side by side.

00:17:00.240 --> 00:17:03.639
You were required to get on your knees and worship.

00:17:03.640 --> 00:17:08.469
I saw these massive screens—huge screens all on the side

00:17:08.470 --> 00:17:10.480
of the buildings of these courthouses.

00:17:14.559 --> 00:17:18.949
On Fridays, he would appear wherever you

00:17:20.520 --> 00:17:23.279
were. If it was America or Europe or whatever, you would go to this place of

00:17:23.280 --> 00:17:25.519
worship on Fridays and look at

00:17:25.520 --> 00:17:27.599
the screen.

00:17:27.600 --> 00:17:31.199
They would worship him at those screens and it was

00:17:31.200 --> 00:17:32.479
all over the place, but they were always

00:17:32.480 --> 00:17:33.839
in white robes. They were always in these

