00:29:41.279 --> 00:29:46.398
must not take the mark."And when he

00:29:46.399 --> 00:29:50.239
said that,

00:29:50.240 --> 00:29:55.350
they cut his head off right there. And I'm talking it

00:29:56.880 --> 00:29:59.918
fell and rolled at my feet, and I could smell his blood. That's how

00:29:59.919 --> 00:30:05.430
awful it was. Jesus stood there with me

00:30:05.679 --> 00:30:09.830
the whole time, and he never made a comment about it. He just told me to

00:30:11.679 --> 00:30:14.479
look. And so I looked and I watched the woman, and she said, "I'll take the

00:30:14.480 --> 00:30:16.719
mark. I'll take it. I'll take the

00:30:16.720 --> 00:30:19.599
chip.

00:30:19.600 --> 00:30:22.558
Don't take their heads."And

00:30:22.559 --> 00:30:25.119
this is what is so incredible; it's

00:30:25.120 --> 00:30:29.398
absolutely amazing about this part. They take this chip, and

00:30:29.399 --> 00:30:33.350
instantaneously those children were

00:30:34.480 --> 00:30:37.278
