00:30:45.279 --> 00:30:50.278
the chip, the baby, the two children, and

00:30:50.279 --> 00:30:52.359
her instantaneously lose

00:30:52.360 --> 00:30:55.199
emotion.

00:30:55.200 --> 00:30:57.038
They don't have any emotion on their face.

00:30:57.039 --> 00:31:00.879
They totally lose the crying.

00:31:00.880 --> 00:31:02.879
It's like they went like a zombie right there

00:31:02.880 --> 00:31:05.199
in front of me. Their minds and

00:31:05.200 --> 00:31:07.759
everything had a peace again. It's like

00:31:07.760 --> 00:31:11.719
the chip sent a peace

00:31:11.720 --> 00:31:16.079
to their brain somehow. I don't know how; all I

00:31:16.080 --> 00:31:20.630
