00:32:05.840 --> 00:32:10.230
understand how. All I know is that chip produced some kind of signal, some

00:32:11.279 --> 00:32:15.230
kind of endorphin somehow, and calmed his mind down, and

00:32:15.760 --> 00:32:18.558
instantaneously he became calm and he did not jump off that bridge. It knew;

00:32:18.559 --> 00:32:21.038
I don't know how it knew that you

00:32:21.039 --> 00:32:25.269
were fixing to do something like that.

00:32:25.760 --> 00:32:28.388
Then I would see people mowing their grass and I would walk by them, but they couldn't see

00:32:28.389 --> 00:32:30.399
