00:33:35.039 --> 00:33:38.719
They would kill you right there—no

00:33:38.720 --> 00:33:42.239
questions. If you didn't take it, they'd cut your head off.

00:33:42.240 --> 00:33:45.199
There was a woman—I

00:33:45.200 --> 00:33:48.079
remember her face. She was a white

00:33:48.080 --> 00:33:50.558
woman with brown hair, and she was

00:33:50.559 --> 00:33:53.119
